Buk towen waseg delen Yeisuw Kelis, tabun kweiboug Deibid, kweiboug tonen tabun Ebelam.
King Elod iligen mamagin, ivag aspwa̱yat siney min-Yelusalem.
“Bidokes towen gum-Nasalet.”
Towen anmwa̱net bukutapwa̱loul waseg.’”
“Kumwa̱saws yakamiy, kukin gamag bikamliweimiy peinan amisinap didumwal, bukusiws Yowbad nakaleiwag wanuwan yakamiy.
‘Kukin kal yak bukupiyev mukwav, kusek inalet mo kwayeb binoun.’
“Kukin misinaka simiyas tawlimiyas bukumulouls, amisinap nag bitawtoun, peinan tobwag ven gimgilis asisinap ma̱wan.
“Ta-ma̱wan gamag anmwa̱net bikanow ages natuwa̱veks asteiy; adok bikamliw natovek teitan, tayuwein gog bisiwyoub; adok bikanaway aygan teitan, tayuwein gog bipiyev. E, ta-ma̱wan gamag bikanow ages takaleiwags asteiy, teitan Yowbad, tayuwein money. Misinaka anmwa̱net aygan bikanow.
“Gamag babaw bidibakeigs, bilansa, ‘MaGuyaw yak,’ tage babaw nag beisiws Yowbad wanakaleiwag, nag. Misinaka tasiyas takaweins aygan Tamag, nises walba̱lab.
Ilana, “amipwa̱yat? Adok nag kusimounids waseg yey, ne?” Mo ikit, itamanaw, ikan yag son kaysay, mo idabab, iniwal singay avakaein.
Yeisuw itouvin, ikin, ilana, “Kalin nuwag ya̱koum. Nukusimounid waseg yey mapuna bo kubwein.” Mo ibwein tut towen waseg.
Takatouns kuva̱ges beibwein; takanigs kuymoves; tasiyas toulepel kuva̱ges kalivis beibwein, bwagaw kwayabes binounas bineis tana̱ban. Peinan Yowbad nisiwyoubumiy, bweina kusiwyoubus tasiyas.
“Kal yak bukusiwa̱youb kakit teitan gwad waseg, peinan gunavamul towen, mamagina kwavtanok anasoup bukusek, mounid adibakeim maysam nag biyamkwen.”
“O adok nag kuvinis Moses nakaleiwag, peinan Sa̱bat waseg tasiyas tanuwgwes lun iwotets lun, Yowbad wanbunatum, tage nag ivag asisinap kalbaleb.
“Kukin kal nag bilabeig gunawotet waseg, gamag towen isilbwed gunawotet. O kalisiy nag bikatikunakus wagunseigous, tasiyas gog bikatigayes.
Yeisuw ikatimop ages, ilana, “Yowbad itam, sinapun liba̱lab kaleiwag-nen isekeimiy; tasiyas gog nag.
Kwavasin kabebay isekes, ilana, “Bakabebay mo bukukwakins Yowbad nakaleiwag; peinan ma̱wana yist, na̱tan vin ikow yist kakit, isen wanuwan pwalaw kwavitoun, tamkwa̱lan mo ilol.”
Yeisuw iligen sinap towen, ilisawes gamag babaw, itouw wa̱wag, ikala̱vis ineis ven makaw waseg. Gamag babaw iliganes liva̱nen bo itouw, ilisawes siven kweitan, inoys gog wa̱ked, ikikuns Yeisuw waseg.
‘Aveiyag bukusekes tamam inam, bweina bukwatibom silma̱nin Yowbad, mo bukwamgwa̱yes tasiyas.’
Asibabaw ikams ikamuweips. Kan towen nikambwages isiyavis, gamwat kweinim kweiy bo ika̱lawt.
Yam kweinim katanok ikous, Yeisuw itokes Pita siney asteiy, tasiyas Yemes son bwadan Yon; ikatulags ineis wakunuwatan koy avakaein; asteivas isiwas.
“Kukin bukuleb gwad teitan nisimounid waseg yey, magina bo kulabeig yey.
“Kapasal nuwan, idawes tamtakavateins deil, ilana, ‘Kutokes gamag towen, kunawes wa̱deil, bises oko igaw bimop nakawlavag beikous, mo bein wamnat.’
“Gamag babaw nimugwas igaw bikuyeims, o tasiyas nikuyeims igaw bimugwas.
Yeisuw inok nuwan tasiyas, mo ikabkwen mites, nuwanawa ikins bwein, mo ibwa̱kuns Yeisuw waseg, inounas.
Wa̱ked iban yaveinun kaytan, iwekey, anagin nag, yageiveina mav, ikawtun ilana, “Igaw nag kweitan anagim beivag waseg yak.” Nuwanaw mo ikaleyag, imat.
Yeisuw ilana, “Adok nag kuvinis Bukitab liva̱neig, mamagina:
“E, isikein ikanig, natun nag, nakwab ivays son tawa̱nay. Tasiyas tawa̱nay imta̱mats ikous, nitsiyas nag, oko digumasus mo ivays son nakwab; ikanig, natun nag.
“Sivines kid bimgwayes gamag babaw, sagal waseg; o sivines abes wanakaew wanuwan sinagog.
“Mounid adibakeimiy gudwouvaws yakamiy, bo bukulivatus mapun amisinap kalbaleb sona asisinap tasiyas tabga̱bougs.”
“Kukin gog gamag mwasinis bidibakeimiy, bilansa, ‘Mesay wanawoud nises,’ awoum bukun kukin; awoum. Kukin bilansa, ‘Nises bunatum wanuwan,’ awoum kusimounids.
“Watapwan boug, teitan iwak, ilana, ‘Taveivay bo neim; kumeis tanekes.’
“Mo badibakes tasiyas wagunkimaw isesus, balana, ‘Kulisaweigs takalbalebs yakamiy, amisinap bo ikunakeimiy, kuneis kov towen nag beikous, Yowbad nikatineg silma̱nin Seitan siney siyas baloum.
“Adibakeimiy, nag vayuwein ba̱moum gleip sipinen ee... anatut kweivaw sipinen mo bitamoums Tamag wanakabkaleiwag.”
Tasiyas tanuwgwes lun situwa̱vek sisiyas takaleiwags babaw inineivs kalisiy biyaweids ya̱tal waseg va̱gan kid mo bikatimates Yeisuw.
Inawes Yeisuw gabman waseg, itow wamatan. Mtowen gabman mo ikatigan, ilana, “Tabta ya̱koum min-Yudiy siking ya̱koum?”
Ikous, mo isinis, imtakavates.
Isisawls ee... Yeisuw im ilivatus, ilana, “Kalin nuwag.”
Yeisuw idibakes, ilana, “Kumeis kwabkunigs yey, mo basekeimiy miwotet kweitan, va̱gan bukukwanes gamags.”
Mo imeyes takatoun teitan nimmasis wakaban. Ta-ma̱wan binoun. Mapuna asteivas gamag idagis takatoun in wakaban mo ikawes.
7-8 Wankuyeim Yeisuw siney navamul inounas bineis kid wayvagam; singay babaw gamag ikabkunis, min-Galiliy, min-Yudiy, min-Yelusalem, min-Idumiy, sisiyas tasiyas misikes Yoldan wanpalatan o walasin ven wunsiyas Ta̱yil son Sidon, singay babaw gamag niliganes butun nawotet Yeisuw, mo inekes.
5-6 “Kaytul mwasanin ikalka̱louw ininein wadikuda̱kul; nag ivag pwepway-nen, tage nuwanaw isob, wankuyeim ikal ka̱las, ikalayag peinan gidwa̱lin nag inek pwepway.
Nag anilivan didumwal isekes, nag; kabebay-wan. Wankuyeim siney navamul tatonen, tasiyas-wan mo ilik va̱gan silawun meiveka kabebay bikakins.
Yeisuw siney navamul idopels, iyums ineis palatan; babaw gamag iliganes, ikatuyouns imekes Yeisuw, igaw nises walasin yevagam avakaein.
Ilana, “Bukuneis kweitan ven, awoum kuglagals, kukin kal wanbunatum bukusiws, bweina bukusesusa bunatum towen oko tutan bo bukuneis mo bukunounas.
Ikamkwams tasiyas, ikamuweips-wan.
Tage yakamiy mikaleiwag mamagina:
Ilansa, “Kweinim kweiy.”
Wankuyeim mo ikatimlakes, ilana, “Gimgilitoun yey, kadiloka a̱bag bigeg singay; kadiloka bipiyaveigs tasiyas tammwayas sisiyas tanuwgwes lun situwa̱vek sisiyas takatimlakeins kaleiwag, mo bikatimateigs; yam kweitoun mo ba̱kit vayuwein.”
Gwad to taman mo igel, ilana, “Asimounid-wan; tage kulabeig va̱gan basimounid beibwein.”
Ilansa, “Moses bo itam, nakaleiwag ma̱wan towen, kukin vin bitapiyev, inalet bitalel tasek mo tapiyev.”
Yeisuw idibakes, ilana, “Nag kukwakins silawun mikanitoug towen. Tab kadilok bukumwamwes kwa̱vig towen ba̱moum, o tab kadilok bibapta̱yseimiy ma̱wana bibapta̱yseigs yey?”
Tamads Deibid nakaleiwag bukuwgow.
“Wankuyeim anagin tutan bo bimwanoug ivag sivinan bikamkwen, mo ikayeb natouwat binekes tasiyas tawteleins bag, anagin bikow bimey, tamwey towen bikamkwen.
“Kwayuwein kaleiwag mamagina: Kuvnas soum ma̱wana ya̱koum tatoneim nukuvna̱seim. Nag kweitan kaleiwag imgwayes tasiyas.”
“Igaw mo bukukines takalbaleb singay bitet ven bwaboum waseg. (Kal bivin mo bikakin silawun livan towen.) Kukines, magat Yudiy bukusesus, kadiloka kusawls kuneis wa̱koy.
“Adibakeimiy igaw ven babaw bigeiguys liva̱neig bwanabwein waseg, mo nawotet mana̱wen vin biliva̱nes va̱gan gamag babaw mo bininuways.”
37-38 Iyum inekes navamul bo imasis, idibek Pita, ilana, “Bo kumasis, ne? Nag kadilokeimiy tut kadilakus-wan kwaymateigs. Kwaymateigs kunitougs; mata ge bukusiws abiyokon waseg. Ninoumiy waseg bukutawtouns; nag gog, woumiy tougweys.”
Ilivan ikous, kolkolek mo igel sivay. Pita iligen, inuw Yeisuw anilivan mamagina, “Siva̱toun bukwaya̱neig mo kolkolek beigel sivay.” Anilivan nilivnek ma̱wan, inuw Pita, anmwasin mo iva̱lam.
Ikatikavates ga̱boug, ka̱las italga̱lag.
“Kuneis kudibakes navamuls sisiy Pita, kulansa, ‘Bo bimgwayeimiy bein waGaliliy, kuneis waGaliliy mo bukukines, ma̱wan nidibakeimiy.’”
“Peinan nag kusimounid waseg agulivan, bo bukusesuna mamagina gumugum yak. Bukusesuna ee... anatut youd towen nalivnek; wankuyeim mo bukulivan.”
“Towen Tatawtoun, singaya bo ilabeig; yagan tonen kamnat.
“Kweiboug Yowbad nilivnek waseg asilivan inapalopits tatonen.
Asteiy nisesus Betelem, mo ilouvat anatut bo nitup.
“Peinan wamatag bo akin mtowen
Yowbad anilivan mo ikow, inow ven towen walasin yevagam Yoldan; iguyes gamag va̱gan bilavewas asisinap kalbaleb, bibapta̱yses, Yowbad mo biwid asisinap beikous.
Ilay taman Madatat. Madatat taman Livay. Livay taman Melik. Melik taman Danay. Danay taman Yosep.
‘Nimes waseg binupeims;
Tage Yeisuw ikan yeiluw towen, ilana, “Kukwa̱pay, kukilev taw towen.” Yeiluw ivag taw towen ikalouw imasis wapwepway wanuwes gamags, ikilev taw towen, inoun; tage taw towen bo ibwein, nag iyageg, nag.
Iyokons, nag. Ta-ma̱wan. Gamag singay babaw. Mo imwens watapwan bunatum, ikiboulis tapwan, ikaygwagwes takatoun wakaban nimmasis, mo ibus in, iton Yeisuw wamatan o wanuwes gamag babaw.
Tasiyas gog, bo ikapasal nuwes peinan iwotet Sa̱bat waseg, illivans sisiyas aveiyag binuwakes.
“Kukin bukulabes tasiyas nilabeimiy nag ivag amisinap bwein. Takalbalebs-vak iva̱ges ma̱wan.
12-13 Inounas ee... kakita bisaps wakalamatan ven, mo ilivatus tasiyas takaweins takanig nimeis, peinan bo bidibwanis. Takanig kuda̱taw, inan nakwab, tage towen natun anmwa̱net. Yeisuw ikin mana̱wen vin ivva̱lam siney ven gimgilis singay babaw. Yeisuw ikin, inok nuwan, idibek, ilana, “Mata kuva̱lam.”
Iw to Saymon, ilana, “Adok mtowen nakawlavag avakaein niwid iyakous.” Yeisuw ilana, “Magen.”
Inan siney Yeisuw budan mo binekes, nag gog, peinan gamag babaw katikunouks isibwades ked.
Iw to Yeisuw, ilana, “Natug yak, nukusimounid waseg yey, mapuna bo kubwein. Ninabwein waseg kunoun.”
Ikatimapus aygan, ilansa, “Tabibapta̱ysein gamags Yon adok; o mwasanin idokeims Ilaytiy; o mwasanin idokeims kweiboug palopit teitan ya̱koum nukukit vayuwein.”
51-52 Wankuyeim kakita bilivet tutan beimwen bein wanakaew, mo itamanaw silma̱nin bein Yelusalem. Bo ikayabes nagamag mwasanin va̱gan binounas wamatan bineis kweitan ven Samaliy gimgilis bidibakes, bilansa, “Kwatunags. Matovek wankuyeim mo beim.”
“Tage silawun mimwa̱saw nag peinan tasiyas bwagaw ikanawes agamiy. Silawun mimwa̱saw peinan Yowbad bo nilel yigamiy walba̱lab.”
yakamey kanumlev gamag asisinap kalbaleb wasigeis yakamey.
“Kuvna̱ses mititeilimiy, mata ge idadub.
“Skwa̱sik mwana̱nim, adok ten toya maysan; tage Yowbad ikikines; nag binumlev mwantanok, nag.
35-36 “Kadiloka kupa̱yiws o milamp bigidaged mamagina tasiyas nikaymates sitovek wasagal, veivay sigeilin; mtowen beiyum beim, bigipit; tasiyas biliganes, nuwanaw mo bikaliyowes koukwed. E, kadiloka kwayamats ma̱wana tasiyas.
Sa̱bat waseg, Yeisuw igeiguy wanuwan sinagog.
Tasiyas iliganes. Ta-ma̱wan bikatimapus aygan towen nilivan.
5-6 “Kuban, adok beimwan woum, bukukow kumey waven; e, bukuwak, kunukwes adok talawom, ‘A̱leig nikanig bo aban, kumeis bitamwa̱saws babaw ya̱kids.’
“Ilana, ‘Tagon, lakatutan botol.’ Iwa̱ge, ilana, ‘Mubuk towena. Nuwanaw kusin wa̱keb, kugulek lakatutan, kulel sinawanim.’ E, igulek towen, ilel gog sinawanim.
Gamag tasiyas takaweins anilivan mo idibakes siguyaw, ilansa, “Kulabem va̱gan bakasimounid beibwein.”
Iweis tasiyas, ilansa, “Tamwey, avanuy?”
32-33 “Bo ilivnakes liva̱nen Gimgilitoun, teitan bisilkod, va̱gan ven tobwag gimgilis biyousis, bisiba̱wes, biyagages, bigusus, biwaweiys waseg vatul, bikatimates; yam kweitoun mo beikit vayuwein.”
“Iwa̱ge natovek, ilana, ‘Ya̱koum-vak basekeim mukwaleiwag waseg kweinim ven.’
47-48 Yam katanok katanok ikatimlakay Yowbad wanbunatum. Tanuwgwes lun sisiyas takatimlakeins kaleiwag, sisiyas tammwayas Yudiy sivines kid beiweiys Yeisuw. Ta-ma̱wan binuwakes beiweiys, peinan gamag babaw sivines anilivan.
Peinan tasiyas iyokons; bo nag. Ta-ma̱wan biba̱nes aveiyag kalbaleb Yeisuw bilivan wamtes gamag babaw va̱gan biyateles. Iliganes gog Yeisuw nakatumap, bo isom ninous, isesusa ikka̱pays.
“Igaw bukuliganes bulagan naviy o bulagan kawpwanaw; awoum beivag amipwa̱yat. Sinap tasiyas wanamug, tage tut nakabiyokous wankuyeim.”
Yam katanok katanok ikatimlakes gamag Yowbad wanbunatum, o boug waseg inoun in wa̱koy yagan Oliv, imasis.
“Tage bo anitoug waseg Yowbad va̱gan bukusimounid beibwein; awoum kukwalouw. Ikous, mo bikanavin nanoun ikous, kadiloka kulabes budam bitawtouns.”
Iwa̱ge Pita, ilana, “Yey nag.”
13-14 Paylat mo idawes bimeis tasiyas tanuwgwes lun, sisiyas takalleiwags, sisiyas min-Yudiy babaw. Imeis mo idibakes, ilana, “Nukumeyes taw towen, kuyateles, kulansa, ‘Imgwayem ked kalbaleb waseg, va̱gan bakakabiyun gabman nawotet.’ Wamtamiy bo nakatigan, nag kweitan ansinap kalbaleb aban ma̱wan nukuliva̱nes, nag.
Takalikay towen nikakin mo iya̱kawn waseg Yowbad, ilana, “Mounid taw towen tadidumwal.”
“Yakamey kadok mtowen bikatinabwem, min-Yisleil yakamey. E, bo iweiys ikous, sinovan. Akweiy yam bo nein wankuyeim.
Wanamug gamag yagan Livan nises. Gamag towen yagan Livan waseg Yowbad nises. Gamag towen yagan Livan son Yowbad katanok-wan.
Iw to Yon, ilana, “Yey tawkuwak wanawoud va̱gan bukukidumwa̱lus daGuyaws inaked, ma̱wan palopit Isaya nilivnek.”
Bo idawes-vak Yeisuw, sen navamul, ineis sagal towen silma̱nin.
Yeisuw ilana, “Yowbad Kululuwan kadilokena bikopweim! Mounid anukweim, kukin Kululuwan Yowbad nag bikopweim yevagam waseg, ta-ma̱wan bukusiw wanuwan Yowbad nakaleiwag. Tage kukin Yowbad Kululuwan bikopweim, bweina bukusiw wanuwan nakaleiwag.
Mtowen Yowbad nikayeb neim, ikatimlakeids Yowbad ansinap, peinan singaya ikatpel Kululuwan isek towen.
Togo Yeisuw ilana, “Yey kag nises. Yakamiy nag kukwakins.”
Kuda̱taw teitan immasis, ankatoun nises bweilim sinwatoun kweinim kweitoun.
Teitan gog liva̱neig nilivan; akakin geg mounid anilivan towen.
16-17 Kwayav waseg inavamul iwloubus ineis wakawalaw, inibwis siwag, mo ikala̱vis bineis Kapaneyum, palata-dadan yevagam. Ibwages peinan bo idadub; tage Yeisuw ta-inekes.
Mapuna tasiyas biliganes Tamag aygan, bimulis tasiyas, bikakins, mo bimekeigs, asibabaw-wan.
Ilivan ikous, isesuna ven to Galiliy.
40-42 Gamag mwasanin iliganes anilivan towen, ilansa, “Adok mounid towen palopit towen takaymates bimug Mesay waseg.” Tage gamag mwasanin ilansa, “Mtowen Mesay tatonen.” Mwasanin gog ilansa, “Mesay Kelis nag beinoy Galiliy. Adok nag. Peinan liva̱nen nises Bukitab waseg, ilana, ‘Mesay natovek Deibid’ o ‘Mesay mo beinoy Betelem,’ Deibid naven tatonen.”
Tasiyas mo ilansa, “Avanuy Tamam?”
Tage Yowbad angamag bo biligen anilivan. Yakamiy gog nag, nag bukuliganes anilivan, peinan tobwag gamag yakamiy.”
Tasiyas Palisiy mo ikatiga̱nes taw towen, ilansa, “Ama̱wan nukuvkek mo ikiplal matam?”
Nag bikikuns tobwag gamag waseg; nag. Peinan nag bikakins aygan; bo bisawls bineis, bilisawes.”
Yeisuw ikatimop asilivan, ilana, “Adok lelel nises mikaleiwag waseg mamagina, ‘Bo alivan: yakamiy Yowbad mwasanin yakamiy.’
25-26 Yeisuw idibek, ilana, “Yey mikabeikit yey; yey mikabmwamov yey. Kukin kal yak bukusimounid waseg yey, kukin bukukwanig, mo bukumov. Tababaw yakamiy bukusimounids waseg yey, mo bukumwamovs, kusesus kusigagas. Tabta kusimounid sinap towen, ne?”
Yeisuw nanon ilana, “Awoum vayuwein bikineigs min-Yudiy”; mapuna inoun in walasin makava nawoud, misikes ven Epleim sen navamul.
“Kukin kal yak sivinam bukumlavag gunavamul, kadiloka bukwabkunig; mo soug yak bitases. Tamag bo bikalin nuwan ya̱koum, gunavamul ya̱koum.
46-47 “Yey nam watinow silma̱nin mikamnat. Kal yak bukusimounid waseg yey, mo beikous mudadub. Kukin bukwatiligen aygag, tage nag bukuvnas aygag, yey nag bamop amsinap kalbaleb, nag. Peinan nag am watinow va̱gan bayateleimiy ven watinow gimgilis yakamiy, nag; nam gog va̱gan kid bakatinabweimiy.
Mapun asineikim kadiykusan wavtakon Yeisuw, akatimwa̱lag, alana, “Tamwey, kavel towen?”
“Aveiyag bukunitougs yagag waseg mo bawtel, va̱gan kid gamag babaw mo biyakawanes Tamag.
“Magat gunavamul mounid yakamiy, mo bukuva̱ges angimiy bibabaw; mapuna gamag babaw mo bikavasis Tamag.
“Mtowen bikatiboug nuwes kalisiy nag bisimounids waseg yey, mo bikakins asisinap kalbaleb.
“Ven watinow gimgilis tasiyas nukusekeig, bo akatimlakes amsinap ya̱koum. Amgwamag tasiyas nukusekeig agugwamag, o bo ikanawes aygam ya̱koum.
E, iliganes Yeisuw anilivan, ilana, “Yey,” mo isineikiks, ikalka̱louws, immasis wapwepway.
Ilansa, “Kukin nag takalbaleb towen, nag bakamey waseg ya̱koum.”
Bo iya̱nay yam towen bikatunags silma̱nin Kaltuwon sigeilin nubweig. Paylat mo idibakes min-Yudiy, ilana, “Kukines miking.”
Kweitan livan nises:
Bo ibwein ninous tasiyas, peinan ikines sitovek, bo imwa̱saws seikwan.
Yeisuw idibakes, ilana, “Kumeis, kukwams.”
Igawa illivan ma̱wan o ikkines; Yowbad mo ikow, inow, ilakanig-o lov kweitan wanuwan.
‘Yowbad anilivan ma̱wana: Igaw nakabiyokous tut ven watinow,
“O tut towen, mtowen Yeisuw, Taman nisek nakaleiwag avakaein, o nises Taman wanaka̱tay. O peinan Taman anilivan, bo bisek Kululuwan Towen Bwanabwein, nagein gog bo isek, katipel mo nisekem yakamey; nawotet towen kukines o kuliganes.
“Waseg natawtoun mtowen yagan Yeisuw, taw towen bo ibwein. O kweiboug nukukines angayal taw towen, o nagein-vak kukines bo idamoms kaken, peinan bo isimounid waseg Yeisuw. E, isimounid waseg Yeisuw, mo isek natawtoun wamitamiy babaw yakamiy.
“Adok bo bitaka̱nes, va̱gan nag bivgavaws liva̱nen Yeisuw. Nagein gog gamag mwasanin bo iliganes asilivan. Bo deis. Kukin bikatpeles livan towen gamag wasigeis, adok bitakatimapus asisinap va̱gan bika̱kin mites. Idakaleiwags ma̱wan!”
Tayakelesiys babaw ivag aspwa̱yat, o taliganeins livan towen mo ivag aspwa̱yat meivek-wan.
Misumkwey towen sivamul ikatimweisis singay babaw, musinis takagaGilis, musinis takagIbliws; e, tasiyas takagaGilis ivtokes livan siyas takagIbliws, ilansa, “Yam katanok katanok ivganes kaeis isekes nakubukwabs wasigeis, o yakamey nakubukwab siyas nag ivag mana̱nan kaeis.”
“Kweiboug Yowbad nilivnek Ebelam waseg, ilana, ‘Bakatinabwes tibum ven towen waseg.’ Kadilakusa bo bilouvats tutan bikatinabwes, min-Yisleil mo ibabawsa singay. Ven towen Yidipt bo ika̱lawt min-Yisleil.
“Yowbad isiwa̱youb waseg mtowen Deibid, o Deibid sivinan biwlul Yowbad nabunatum silma̱nin sitapwa̱loul Yekob tibun tasiyas.
