Kukin bukumuloul soum mo bukuleb nawotet kalbaleb waseg.
Tage gamag tasiyas neisiws wasigeis yakamiy, asisinap ma̱wan kalbaleb, ikammikons mo ivag asisinap kalbaleb, waseg iyagages wous tatineis. Kaleiwag ipiyaves. Iyages-vak min-liba̱lab tasiyas takamnats.
